cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SI, cs.CR, cs.MM

The paper deals with information-theoretic performance limits for broadcast channels with side-information, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses the use of these channels in cellular downlink communications (cs.NI), two-way relay communications (cs.SI), and secure wireless broadcasting (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper presents inner and outer bounds for the achievable rate region, which involves mathematical analysis and optimization (cs.MM).
